Text: giddayJeff Survived my trip back and a week alone with the kiddies while Nina was out at her conference in Corsica Just got notified that the first film I sent off to shutterfly is available There are some really great photos from the wedding day Im sending you the link by separate email if youre interested and will make copies of the likely photos for you and rebecca once Ive gotten all the rolls processed If you see any in particular that you like let me know and Ill get copies made of those too Theres a really good one of the two of you with Shukran I really enjoyed hanging out with both of you and am looking forward to seeing you one of these days in SF I dont have rebeccas email Please sent her my love All the best Misha Weidman ChiliUp
